{"tid":1865322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛秘書長狂言護中國，民進黨正妹立委賴品妤：你韓國瑜嗎","createTime":"2020-02-06T06:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T16:31:27.000Z","uid":52658,"like":185,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2587eac4b67592aee2e4cd3d0d3ae6a49490d3","tid":1865322,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"中國大陸近期爆出武漢肺炎「2019新型冠狀病毒」（2019-nCoV），疫情持續擴散，但世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）在疫情發生後卻不斷偏袒中國，昨（5）日被問到中國是否在第一時間隱匿疫情，他表示，無法說明中國有或沒有隱匿通報。<br />\n<br />\n對此，民進黨立委賴品妤今日痛批，「這回答跟高雄市長韓國瑜有什麼兩樣？世衛韓國瑜嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n民進黨立委范雲也表示，如果台灣防疫做得好，最後將會證明，不是我們需要世界衛生組織，是世界衛生組織需要台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUqyu8z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUqyu8z.jpg&h=ae317b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hV25mfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhV25mfh.jpg&h=ea144e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88bNzAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88bNzAi.jpg&h=373aa9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsfVJtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsfVJtE.jpg&h=cfecaaa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2GRgOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2GRgOF.jpg&h=832e2fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8w3zY11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8w3zY11.jpg&h=40a050f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bd719942ddb1bd39a49ae052b0086cce1d3b112","tid":1865322,"uid":262093,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"人哋而家剪短咗頭髮啦"},{"pid":"53843507db6b9e2fa3d2812cf2cdace2325afca5","tid":1865322,"uid":52658,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"8bd719942ddb1bd39a49ae052b0086cce1d3b112","tid":1865322,"uid":262093,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"ci